Author
Created by Ananya Kawley
Description
Job Manager is a simple tool that allows you to:

Track multiple jobs with detailed information
Record worker names, job categories, hours worked, and payment rates
Store and retrieve job data using CSV files
Calculate total earnings automatically

Features

Add Jobs: Create job entries with name, category, hours, rate, and date
Save to File: Export all job data to a CSV file for persistent storage
Load from File: Import previously saved job data from CSV files
Data Validation: Ensures all job information is properly formatted
Easy Testing: Includes comprehensive test suite for reliability

Requirements
Python 3.6 or higher
pytest

CSV File Format
The CSV file follows this structure:
name,category,hours,rate,date
Alice,Cleaning,4,15,13/11/2025
Bob,Gardening,5,20,14/11/2025